 Risks & Constraints

 - Budget: Extra GPU dispatch for column probes adds ~2-5ms (same order as row probing)
 - Do NOT re-add CDF-adaptive spacing — removed in v16.10 for good reason (density bands)
 - Do NOT re-add cdt2d — removed in v11.1 (O(n^2), 12+ min at production scale)
 - Chain linking: The existing linkFeatureChainsByKind should work for T-direction features without changes, since column features are injected into per-row feature arrays before linking
